                                        BUSINESS QUESTION
Which customers are generating the most revenue, and how can we retain them?

                       QUERY
SELECT
*
FROM ecommerce_data
ORDER BY lifetime_value DESC
LIMIT 10;


Insight:
These are the top 10 customers contributing the most revenue. The business is currently relying on a small group of high-value customers,
which can be risky if any of them stop purchasing


Recommendation
We should strengthen retention for these customers by giving them better experience like faster service, early access to products, and highlighting
their importance. At the same time, we should also focus on converting more customers into high-value customers.
